{"tid":291994,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人想一齊學口琴？","createTime":"2017-06-21T04:06:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-04T00:35:50.000Z","uid":1277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f2928846d711f697dc6653068740903e13bdb12d","tid":291994,"uid":1277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T04:06:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.parklandmusic.com.hk/music-course/harmonica/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.parklandmusic.com.hk%2Fmusic-course%2Fharmonica%2F&d=JydjAett6ydDo5rJC82wtsn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=ab8207c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.parklandmusic.com.hk/music-course/harmonica/</a><br />\n<br />\n上網見到有d 口琴 course係二人同行一人免費<br />\n但毒撚無乜朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以上黎睇下有無人都有興趣今個暑假一齊黎學下口琴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nTg:@xcmyeung"},{"pid":"3d793ed80670c6294d611fe6ad3a658de57ac711","tid":291994,"uid":41008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T04:56:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://www.parklandmusic.com.hk/music-course/harmonica/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.parklandmusic.com.hk%2Fmusic-course%2Fharmonica%2F&d=JydjAett6ydDo5rJC82wtsn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=ab8207c9\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.parklandmusic.com.hk/music-course/harmonica/</a><br />\n<br />\n上網見到有d 口琴 course係二人同行一人免費<br />\n但毒撚無乜朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以上黎睇下有無人都有興趣今個暑假一齊黎學下口琴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nTg:@xcmyeung</blockquote><br />\n巴打 我係工聯會學緊復音口琴 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"886782946b035efaeae610f4c933931e222af24a","tid":291994,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T04:56:56.000Z","msg":"想學blues"},{"pid":"a522259b9b9a2d85cb62deb1115bb57c78ec5f34","tid":291994,"uid":1277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T05:23:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"http://www.parklandmusic.com.hk/music-course/harmonica/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.parklandmusic.com.hk%2Fmusic-course%2Fharmonica%2F&d=JydjAett6ydDo5rJC82wtsn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=ab8207c9\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.parklandmusic.com.hk/music-course/harmonica/</a><br />\n<br />\n上網見到有d 口琴 course係二人同行一人免費<br />\n但毒撚無乜朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以上黎睇下有無人都有興趣今個暑假一齊黎學下口琴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nTg:@xcmyeung</blockquote><br />\n巴打 我係工聯會學緊復音口琴 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係學複音啊 <br />\n但我之前係自學 有d skill 唔係好了解<br />\n見有時間咪出去系統性地再學過<br />\n巴打加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"012ca63eb446dbae0b7958292be896f3d3bafc0e","tid":291994,"uid":1277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T05:29:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想學blues</blockquote><br />\n我都想啊 <br />\n但唔知點解覺得好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我自己都想學半音階 <br />\n我手頭上淨係得一支複音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b28ac2dd2991f6be9cb2e9751fafc51ef2c004cb","tid":291994,"uid":1277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T08:59:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8d1ea79d5e8087df8f1f6fffea048c3d75ee2be","tid":291994,"uid":67118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T09:31:39.000Z","msg":"半音階得唔得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自學緊但想出去學"},{"pid":"b5e76f3a238069203647c6457b4e342240077974","tid":291994,"uid":75256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T09:34:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"http://www.parklandmusic.com.hk/music-course/harmonica/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.parklandmusic.com.hk%2Fmusic-course%2Fharmonica%2F&d=JydjAett6ydDo5rJC82wtsn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=ab8207c9\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.parklandmusic.com.hk/music-course/harmonica/</a><br />\n<br />\n上網見到有d 口琴 course係二人同行一人免費<br />\n但毒撚無乜朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以上黎睇下有無人都有興趣今個暑假一齊黎學下口琴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nTg:@xcmyeung</blockquote><br />\n巴打 我係工聯會學緊復音口琴 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我上年都係工聯會學，但學唔到用條脷頂住d 孔，更加打唔到拍子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d2248c7386896b7ea0e614cf220cf9f572c8512","tid":291994,"uid":1277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T10:21:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>半音階得唔得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自學緊但想出去學</blockquote><br />\n得啊 我都想學<br />\n加我Telegram?<br />\n@xcmyeung"},{"pid":"2ef16bb18605568ade88c3e38a346ff90abb38fa","tid":291994,"uid":1277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T17:05:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de3a5bdb0e5b7d28caaedc8bc1799a49a6f08769","tid":291994,"uid":1277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T04:14:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7dafb80ce5c3d97d45794dd7b043f9c42373880","tid":291994,"uid":1277,"like":0,"dislike"